# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
*.bak
*.backup-*
*.tmp
*.old

# Audit artifacts (generated by audit scans, not for commit)
projects/audit-results/

# Test artifacts (generated by tests, not for commit)
adr/ADR-*-test-*.md
specs/BL-*-test-*.md
specs/PAT-*-test-*.md
specs/INC-*-test-*.md

# AWG/WireGuard client configs (contain private keys, not server configs)
